lead_paragraph: John Isner could have a slight scheduling conflict when he plays his fourth-round match at the Australian Open on Monday — it may coincide with the NFC Championship game being played in the U.S. between the Arizona Cardinals and his beloved Carolina Panthers.

headline.print_headline: Isner Makes 2nd Week at Aussie Open for 1st Time Since 2010
